In order to investigate the effect of fig latex on cell growth HPV expressing cervical cancer cells (CasKi and HeLa), and control HaCaT cells (4 × 103) were seeded in 96 well plate. The following day, cells were treated with various concentrations (0.125, 0.25, 0.5, and 1 µg/ml) of fig latex. After 24, 48 and 72 hours, 20 \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
