To investigate whether the fig latex influences cell growth in cervical cancer by targeting the Ki67 protein, control and cervical cancer cell lines were treated with a non-cytotoxic concentration (0.125 \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
